QuestData.Title: Mudcaked Necklace
QuestData.Description:
<The ancient markings on the necklace are quite difficult to read, but the materials appear to be made of animal hide and carved bone fragments.
Perhaps a knowledgeable hunter may glean insight into this object's value.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Locate someone knowledgeable in plainshunting and handcrafted artifacts.
